de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.bo
Class BOCountry

java.lang.Object
  de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.bo.BOCountry

public class BOCountry
extends java.lang.Object

The business object BOCountry represents a country entity with it's common attributes like name, isoCode or currency. The following example code shows how to create and persist a new country entity. 

 // load a existing currency
 BOCurrency currency = CurrencyBOA.getInstance().findCurrency(TEST_COUNTRY_CURRENCY_CODE);
        
 // ensure that the currency exists
 if (currency != null)
 {
        // create the country
        BOCountry country = new BOCountry();
        country.setIsocode(TEST_COUNTRY_ISOCODE);
        country.setName(TEST_COUNTRY_NAME);
        country.setCurrency(currency);
        CountryBOA.getInstance().saveOrUpdate(country);
 }
